'''Tislit wuccen''' ([[assaɣ ussnan]]: '''Mantis religiosa''') d [[talmest]] n [[aburɣes|ibureɣsen]] yeṭṭafaren [[tislatin wuccen]] deg [[tawacult (tasnudert)|twacult]] n [[talɣemt n yellu|telɣemt n yellu]] .<ref>tilmas n tleɣmatin n yellu (s Teglizit) Mantodea Species File Online [http://mantodea.speciesfile.org/Common/basic/Taxa.aspx?TaxonNameID=1184170 Tislit wuccen ] azemz n unekcum 01 yennayer 2016 {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224213825/http://mantodea.speciesfile.org/Common/basic/Taxa.aspx?TaxonNameID=1184170 |date=24 dujamber 2017}}</ref> Talmest-a tettwaglam-d s talɣa tussnant i tikkelt tamezwarut sɣur [[Carl Von Linné]] deg useggas n [[1758]].

== Ideggan n tudert ==
Azaduɣ aẓaṛan n teslit wuccen iga d [[Turuft|Uruppa]], [[Asya]] yakk d [[Tafriqt|Tferka]]. Akken i yettwasekcem ɣer [[Tamrikt n Ugafa|Temrikt tagafant]] deg useggas n [[1899]] s uɣerrabu i d-yeddmen tiseṭwa n yemɣan i d-ikkan seg unẓul n Uruppa, Tislit n wuccen tga ass-a d azamul amaddud i uwanak n [[Connecticut]]<ref>[http://www.ct.gov/ctportal/cwp/view.asp?a=885&q=246504 CT.gov: The State Insect]; retrieved on August 09, 2010 {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610200539/http://www.ct.gov/ctportal/cwp/view.asp?a=885&q=246504 |date=10 yunyu 2015}}</ref>
